
Please select Delivery or Carry out.
Click reset before clicking between carryout and delivery if customer wants to change options

Type in customer information hit submit to save info to address_book.db
OR
Click "continue to next screen" to move on without saving data

To return to the first window Click the "back to first window" button

To select what pizza you would like click the arrows on the spin boxes or type in a value, when you have made your
selection please hit submit to see your total

If you want to change your order, Click "reset total" to clear your total, be sure to make
 your changes to your order before clicking submit again

You can exit the program anytime by using the "exit program" button in the top left corner of the window
